# Force LF line endings for shell scripts and other text files that get
# baked into Docker images or run on Linux, regardless of OS or editor used
# to create/edit them (prevents "exec /entrypoint.sh: no such file or
# directory" caused by a CRLF shebang line).
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
dockerfile text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
